    About us
</h1>

<div class="info-content-section">
    <div class="info-content">
        <p class="centre-text">
            About 6.8% of Victorians suffer from diabetes, and that number is increasing annually. 
            Here at Diabetes@Home, we believe that proper diabetes management starts at home. 
            Join 5000 Victorians and a professional team of 100 clinicians in combating diabetes.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!--meet the team section-->
    <h3 class="info-header">Meet the team:</h3>
    <div class="info-content">
        <div class="team-images-container">
            <div class="team-image">
                <figure>
                    <img src="/images/team/doctor_1.jpeg">
                    <figcaption>Dr John Doe</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>

            <div class="team-image">
                <figure>
                    <img src="/images/team/doctor_2.jpeg">
                    <figcaption>Dr Harry Doe</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>

            <div class="team-image">
                <figure>
                    <img src="/images/team/doctor_3.jpeg">
                    <figcaption>Dr Jane Doe</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>

            <div class="team-image">
                <figure>
                    <img src="/images/team/doctor_4.jpeg">
                    <figcaption>Dr Emily Doe</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!--display login prompt for guests-->
    {{#unless logged_in}}
        <h3 class="info-header">Login today!</h3>

        <div class="info-content">
            <p>Login to our website to access amazing features such as:</p>
            <ul id="login-features">
                <li>Active Health Monitoring</li>
                <li>Support messages by clinicians</li>
                <li>Competitive diabetes recording</li>
            </ul>
            <p>+ many more!</p> 
        </div>

        <a href="/login_select" class="guest-nav-button">Login here</a>
    {{/unless}}
    
    <img src="/images/login-photo.jpeg" id="login-photo">
</div>